- Berlagak betul.
- Selamat jalan.

127
00:08:01,355 --> 00:08:02,190
Hei.

128
00:08:03,191 --> 00:08:05,443
Kamu berdua dah hilang akal?

129
00:08:06,110 --> 00:08:07,820
Youngjae, si bodoh.

130
00:08:08,321 --> 00:08:11,157
Baik awak buat perubahan yang mereka mahu.

131
00:08:11,240 --> 00:08:12,450
