134
00:08:20,333 --> 00:08:21,542
Awak ingat saya nak…

135
00:08:22,043 --> 00:08:23,044
Sudahlah.

136
00:08:23,127 --> 00:08:25,254
Apa pun, panjangkan segmen

137
00:08:25,338 --> 00:08:28,424
